==Finishing up==
* '''Professor Oddenstein:''' Have you found anything yet?
* '''Player:''' I have everything!
* '''Professor Oddenstein:''' Give 'em here then.
* {{mes|You give the rubber tube, a pressure gauge,}}
* {{mes|and a can of oil to the professor.}}
* '''Professor Oddenstein:''' Let's get this fixed then.
* {{mes|Oddenstein starts up the machine.}}
* {{mes|The machine hums and shakes.}}
* {{Qact|The machine turns Ernest back into human form.}}
* '''Ernest:''' [Thank you sir/Thank you m'lady/Thank you]. It was dreadfully irritating being a chicken. How can I ever thank you?
* '''Player:''' Well a cash reward is always nice...
* '''Ernest:''' Of course, of course.
* {{Qact|Congratulations! Quest complete!}}
